{"tid":1556998,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[政府當內戰？」特首與港鐵及機管局管理層開會　政府：繼續沉着應戰　","createTime":"2019-09-10T02:59:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T03:27:49.000Z","uid":9570,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"964b828307b381a9721391f069cdd118965d1d7a","tid":1556998,"uid":9570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T02:59:33.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥下午與多位司局長、警務處處長以及港鐵公司和機管局管理層舉行會議，總結各方應對示威及破壞行為的經驗，商討日後部署。政府說，與會者對近日持續出現針對機場及港鐵的堵塞及破壞行為感到憤怒，認為違法行為嚴重影響旅客出行及市民日常生活，有損香港形象，絕不能容忍。<br />\n<br />\n當局說，與會者都表示不會受暴力及破壞行為威嚇，將繼續沉着應戰，共同應對，盡力減低示威及破壞行為對市民的影響。林鄭月娥在會上感謝各方多個星期以來堅守崗位，又慰問早前被示威及破壞行為傷及的港鐵員工。<br />\n<br />\n另外，林鄭月娥早上視察港鐵中環站遭受破壞後的損毀情況，她在視察期間與站內市民交談，知道市民對暴徒肆意破壞港鐵設施感到心痛。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479680-20190909.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479680-20190909.htm&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNgCffgmrlYx1zcVg66SIO7I%3D&h=67a554fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479680-20190909.htm&h=d30a6a7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479680-20190909.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6fa4a6d42484720ee885d03a6c6e37962f809a88","tid":1556998,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:00:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">九七移交 承認錯誤 拿出勇氣 奮力一戰 止黑治港</span><br />\nIn 1997 return China is false , Fight for Freedom and Democracy Defend HomeLand of Brave ."},{"pid":"3056c7a8446badc893ed97aea6368d7479d3db29","tid":1556998,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:15:20.000Z","msg":"政權只需要奴隸，唔需要有思考嘅平民"},{"pid":"4bd5bc520eb089df153c8ae538faaaf5becd6e3f","tid":1556998,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:16:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj